   ) ;

--------------------------------------------------------
--  DDL for Table BASE_SPT_XTDJ_TB
--------------------------------------------------------

  CREATE TABLE "BASE_SPT_XTDJ_TB" 
   (	"ID" VARCHAR2(36) DEFAULT SYS_GUID(), 
	"TYPE_ID" VARCHAR2(20), 
	"KEY" VARCHAR2(100), 
	"NAME" VARCHAR2(200), 
	"PARA1" VARCHAR2(200), 
	"PARA2" VARCHAR2(200), 
	"PARA3" VARCHAR2(200), 
	"PARA4" VARCHAR2(200), 
	"CODE" VARCHAR2(20), 
	"MSG" VARCHAR2(200), 
	"BODY" CLOB, 
	"STATE" VARCHAR2(20), 
	"CREATE_USER" VARCHAR2(50), 
	"CREATE_DATE" DATE DEFAULT sysdate, 
	"DATA_COUNT" NUMBER
   ) ;

   COMMENT ON COLUMN "BASE_SPT_XTDJ_TB"."ID" IS '主键ID';
   COMMENT ON COLUMN "BASE_SPT_XTDJ_TB"."TYPE_ID" IS '查询数据类型代码';
   COMMENT ON COLUMN "BASE_SPT_XTDJ_TB"."KEY" IS '接口KEY';
   COMMENT ON COLUMN "BASE_SPT_XTDJ_TB"."NAME" IS '接口名称';
   COMMENT ON COLUMN "BASE_SPT_XTDJ_TB"."PARA1" IS '调用参数值1';
   COMMENT ON COLUMN "BASE_SPT_XTDJ_TB"."PARA2" IS '调用参数值2';
   COMMENT ON COLUMN "BASE_SPT_XTDJ_TB"."PARA3" IS '调用参数值3';
   COMMENT ON COLUMN "BASE_SPT_XTDJ_TB"."PARA4" IS '调用参数值4';
   COMMENT ON COLUMN "BASE_SPT_XTDJ_TB"."CODE" IS '返回消息代码';
   COMMENT ON COLUMN "BASE_SPT_XTDJ_TB"."MSG" IS '返回消息值';
   COMMENT ON COLUMN "BASE_SPT_XTDJ_TB"."BODY" IS '返回数据主体内容';
   COMMENT ON COLUMN "BASE_SPT_XTDJ_TB"."STATE" IS '调用状态：
1-成功，
0-未找到数据，
-1-调用错误';
   COMMENT ON COLUMN "BASE_SPT_XTDJ_TB"."CREATE_USER" IS '创建人';
